data.description: Move in Ready! Newer home nestled on a private dead-end street with lots of trees! 2,160 SF with 4 Bedroom, 2 Bath and Extra Living room or Gameroom! Beautiful spacious kitchen open to the living room with fireplace! Huge island, plenty of counter space and pantry. Oversized owners suite with gorgeous spa bathroom with double sinks! Lots of space and storage. Well maintained. Must see to appreciate!
